
* Web create use AdminCc instead of Requestor

https://devops.netways.de/issues/515

Config option:

# Add users to AdminCc instead of Requestor
Set($RTx_NETWAYS_UserRequestorGroup, 'NETWAYS');

# Preprocess searches to display only with results
#
# Keep in mind that this can cause performance impact on the
# entry page
Set($RTx_NETWAYS_ShowSearchOnlyWithResults, 1);

This changes the create process

* NETWAYS specific tag title

Set($RTx_NETWAYS_EnableTagFormat, 1);

* Confirmation query upon merge

https://devops.netways.de/issues/517

* Show box only if count tickets

* Added classes to boxes:

- netways-tickets-due
- netways-tickets-nobody
- netways-tickets-default

* Changed positions of ShowSummary

* Quick assign of ticket principals

Set($RTx_NETWAYS_EnableQuickAssign, 1);
Set($RTx_NETWAYS_QuickAssignGroup, 'NETWAYS');